name: Scissors-cut paper-wrapped rock X/10000
description:
I found a paper-wrapped rock NFT, right-click-saved it, then cut it with scissors because scissors beats paper.

A commentary on Little Pig's commentary on Pranksy's Rocks, which are a commentary on pfp projects, which you may further comment on by purchasing. This is an idea blockchain, one daisy-chained to the next and I hope someone beats my scissors with rock.
